{"tid":2262732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逸東酒店聘國泰前員工 遭藍絲狙擊 Eaton總經理：感到遺憾","createTime":"2020-10-29T10:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T10:23:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"141ca99cff5ca0d642b551e27e1bda9861419724","tid":2262732,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:23:06.000Z","msg":"早前國泰航空（293）宣佈裁減約5,300名駐港員工，多間機構提出招募計劃吸納人才，其中鷹君（041）旗下逸東酒店（Eaton HK）有份，惟事後被部分網民因政治立場而抵制。逸東酒店今日發聲明指，有關決定無任何政治目的，對創辦人兼總裁羅寶璘（Katherine Lo）被牽連而感到遺憾。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201029/XYO6FXJ66RHNLLQJ7AT73DONH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201029%2FXYO6FXJ66RHNLLQJ7AT73DONH4%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KigKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=d5398c84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201029%2FXYO6FXJ66RHNLLQJ7AT73DONH4%2F&h=0e3e1736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201029/XYO6FXJ66RHNLLQJ7AT73DONH4/</a>"}]}